icial use, you will be asked to provide a CFOAP number for billing as a standard web Announcement. Please send questions about Official messages to publicaffairs@uic.edu .  All Official messages are processed at no charge to the requesting department.   DDDH  DDDH email communications are sent to UIC Deans, Directors, and Department Heads for a flat fee of $35. Administrative-related messages only, please.  We are unable to attach files to DDDH email communications. We can, however, upload a file to the server and place a download link in the message body.   Post the announcement on this date *   Date Format: MM slash DD slash YYYY   at this time *    :  HH     MM     AM  PM    Payment method * CFOAP (campus units) Check (UIC student groups only) CFOAP * Upload image (automatically resized to 1000px wide, set at top of post) File Caption This "caption" area is mandatory for web accessibility. Please describe the image and any text it may contain. This information will be presented as a hidden ALT attribute behind the image. UIC reply-to email address *    Enter Email     Confirm Email    Announcement Title *   Announcement details * Enter your content here. Please don't paste html into this space.  For more information, please contact:   Contact Name (will be published on web) *    First     Last   Contact Email (will be published on web) *   Optional additional contact information (will be published on web) Upload file to distribute with DDDH email Accepted file types: doc, docx. PLEASE NOTE: This file will not be sent as a file attachment. We will upload the file to the web server and provide a download link in the message. Special instructions The UIC Office of Public and Government Affairs has a submission deadline of 3:00 PM CST. Requests sent after this deadline will not be sorted until the following business day. Your submission may be edited for content. *   I have read and understand the above.  Email This field is for validation purposes and should be left